# Handouts

This directory contains curated mathematical handouts from the Drayan Mathematical Series.

The handouts are designed for Olympiad students and focus on developing problem-solving techniques, mathematical maturity, and exposure to classical and modern Olympiad topics.

## Current Handouts

* Drayan Geometry #1
* Drayan Inequalities #1

## Future Topics

* Number Theory
* Algebra
* Combinatorics
* Functional Equations
* Geometry Technique Collections

Each handout contains carefully selected problems, thematic organisation, and professional LaTeX formatting intended for self-study and Olympiad preparation.
